{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f28e6115cf","title":"在志丹陵园红星纪念塔上的题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"963664958d","index":0,"year":1943,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"f28e6115cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bd0f922fa0","type":"paragraph","text":"在志丹陵园红星纪念塔上的题词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"f28e6115cf"},{"id":"e164affc19","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年5月2日）群众领袖民族英雄一一纪念刘子丹间志。我到陕北只和刘志丹同志见过一面，就知道他是一个很好的共产党员。他的英勇轴性，出于意外，但他的忠心耿取为党为国的精神是永远留在党与人民中间，不会磨灭的","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"f28e6115cf"},{"id":"03d2ecf80f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东库环食协民族养馆","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"f28e6115cf"},{"id":"3e0ab9780f","type":"paragraph","text":"华金并子件网程","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"f28e6115cf"},{"id":"70f49927a9","type":"paragraph","text":"程毛泽东为志丹陵园红星纪念塔的题词钟意万龙牵人心中间成指意如，包心的感心万术同点赢","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"f28e6115cf"},{"id":"4abfa3e516","type":"paragraph","text":"坚一个旅好进是求度，他角来原处我到陈兴西和利本开可点观一中应他广八菜","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"f28e6115cf"}],"page":{"id":"5dc0b9221e","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"f28e6115cf","start":27,"end":28}}}},"__N_SSG":true}